'''''Hafrada''''' ('''ההפרדה''') is a [[Hebrew language|Hebrew]] phrase that means "separation" or "[[Apartheid (disambiguation)|apartheid]]". The term has been used by to describe the actual or preferred policies of the [[Israel]]i government in regard to the [[Palestinian people]].


